<a href="https://github.com/cs125-illinois/lecture-webapis-examples"><code>https://github.com/cs125-illinois/lecture-webapis-examples</code></a>
Feel free to fork!</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="sect1">
<h2 id="YOFoQJFHfPmqMQuCPuxoIayFsLopNVWQ">Search Text</h2>
<div class="sectionbody">
<div class="paragraph lead">
<p>Given a line of text, write a function that searches for all occurrences of a
given word.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="sect1 oneword">
